<HEAD>Meese Grand Jury Hears Testimony From Real Estate Magnate</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By MICHAEL J. SNIFFEN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>and</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>JOAN MOWER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writers</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
