building missile from tax forms.</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
 Procrastinators and folks simply trying to forestall the inevitable _ taxes, that is _ made their annual trek to the post office Friday to mail their 1040 forms. `` This happens every year,'' said <PERSON> John </PERSON> <PERSON> Tobias </PERSON>, mail supervisor at the Willkes-Barre, <LOCATION> Pa. </LOCATION>, post office. `` I think it's terrible that people have to wait for the last minute,'' <PERSON> Tobias </PERSON> said. `` People call you today and ask you at the last minute if you have tax forms in your office. And we do n't.'' <PERSON> Dan </PERSON> <PERSON> Jenkins </PERSON> of Mr. Tax of <LOCATION> America </LOCATION> in <LOCATION> Jonesboro </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Ark. </LOCATION>, said at 7 p.m. that his firm had 10 customers left with appointments before the midnight filing deadline. `` My last one is at 8:30, which I expect to finish about 11 p.m.,'' he said. <PERSON> Paul </PERSON> <PERSON> Monroe </PERSON>, regional manager for <ORGANIZATION> H </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION>; R Block in <LOCATION> Boston </LOCATION>, said he sees the same people, year after year, in the waning hours of tax season. `` They look forward to the excitement of April 15th. The adrenalin starts flowing,'' <PERSON> Monroe </PERSON> said. `` It's like a non-contact sport.'' Postal Service consumer advocate <PERSON> Ann </PERSON> <PERSON> Robinson </PERSON> in <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION> said the post office expected to handle 30 million tax returns nationwide in the `` last couple of days'' before the deadline. Post offices across the country were open until midnight to place the all-important April 15 postmark on tax returns, or on envelopes containing Form 4868 requesting an automatic four-month extension of the deadline. `` We expect thousands to be here tonight,'' <LOCATION> U.S </LOCATION>. <ORGANIZATION> Postal </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Service </ORGANIZATION> spokesman <PERSON> Vito </PERSON> <PERSON> F